'''Black 2''' was a [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE fighter]] assigned to [[Black Squadron (Galactic Empire)/Legends|Black Squadron]]. The [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] was flown by [[TIE pilot]] [[Mithel/Legends|"Mauler" Mithel]],<ref name="CCG-Black2" /> and the craft was stationed aboard the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]].<ref name="ANH" />

The [[Cockpit/Legends|cockpit]] had twenty-seven flame emblems on it, each one representing a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] kill. Mithel placed a [[Hologram/Legends|holo]] of his young son, [[Rejlii Mithel|Rejlii]] on the fighter's control yoke.<ref name="CCG-Black2" /> During the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], Black 2 was destroyed after colliding with [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader's]] [[Darth Vader's TIE Advanced/Legends|TIE Advanced]] in the Death Star's [[Meridian trench/Legends|meridian trench]] and subsequently crashing into the trench's wall.<ref name="ANH" />

